methods.add:
Adds an output column.

 To set the inputColumn call nextColumn(String).

:param percentile: (double) - the percentile to calculate
:param resultName: (java.lang.String) - the result name
:return: (io.deephaven.engine.table.impl.by.ApproximatePercentile.PercentileDefinition) a (possibly new) PercentileDefinition
methods.exposeDigest:
If true, the tDigest column is exposed using the given name

:param digestColumnName: (java.lang.String) - the name of the t-digest column in the output
:return: (io.deephaven.engine.table.impl.by.ApproximatePercentile.PercentileDefinition) a (possibly new) PercentileDefinition
methods.nextColumn:
Sets the name of the inputColumn

:param inputColumn: (java.lang.String) - the name of the input column that subsequent calls to add(double, java.lang.String) operate on.
:return: (io.deephaven.engine.table.impl.by.ApproximatePercentile.PercentileDefinition) a (possibly new) PercentileDefinition
methods.setCompression:
